  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003ERoughly 10,000 Baby Boomers will turn 65 years old today and that number will grow as more cross that threshold every day for the next 19 years.\u0026nbsp; As a general population, we are living longer, and continue to stay active well into our 70s, 80s and 90s.\u0026nbsp; As we mature, there are litanies of restrictions that affect our everyday lifestyle, and using NSAIDs and other pharmacological agents to treat aches and pains can leave us with a multitude of side effects.\u0026nbsp; Learn about the benefits of using Super Pulsed Laser, and how these benefits will help us age more gracefully, and allow us to remain active for longer to provide us a better quality of life.\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
